      "role": "user",
      "content": "goblins? i dont know about goblins. it just feels like i'm underwater. everything is quiet and heavy and i'm just so tired of trying to swim up. it feels like there isn't even a surface anymore, just more blackness. i've reached the bottom and i don't think i want to try climbing back up.",
